    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">Which Platform Fits Your AI Needs?</h2>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-navy mb-3 mt-6">For Experts Who Want AI Content Help</h3>
    <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
      <strong>LearnWorlds</strong> and <strong>Teachable</strong> offer the strongest AI content creation among expert-focused platforms. LearnWorlds has the edge on comprehensive AI authoring. Thinkific and Kajabi have useful AI writing assistance but are not as strong for full course generation. Podia lags significantly.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-navy mb-3 mt-6">For Experts Who Want an AI Marketing Assistant</h3>
    <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
      <strong>Kajabi's Creator.io</strong> is the clear winner. No other platform offers a comparable AI chatbot that can engage visitors, answer questions, capture leads, and integrate with your marketing automation.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-navy mb-3 mt-6">For Enterprise Training</h3>
    <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
      <strong>Docebo</strong> is the AI leader for corporate learning — Shape's AI video creation, comprehensive adaptive learning, skill mapping, and predictive analytics make it the most AI-capable enterprise platform. <strong>Absorb LMS</strong> is a strong second choice. <strong>TalentLMS</strong> offers the best AI-to-price ratio for smaller organizations.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-10">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">The Bottom Line</h2>
    <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
      AI capabilities in LMS platforms have matured rapidly between 2024 and 2026, but the gap between platforms has widened. On one end, <strong>Docebo</strong> offers AI that genuinely transforms content creation and delivery. On the other end, <strong>Podia</strong> offers essentially no AI features at all.
    </p>
    <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
      If you're choosing an LMS specifically for its AI features, be clear about what kind of AI you need. Content generation AI helps you build courses faster. Adaptive learning AI helps your learners succeed. Content recommendation AI helps surface the right training at the right time. Analytics AI helps you understand what's working. Few platforms excel at all four. Choose based on which AI capabilities align with your biggest pain point.
    </p>
  </section>

